{"tid":631962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自由黨黨慶CY甩底　 田少捐金牛撐屠狼","createTime":"2018-04-17T03:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T03:33:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a783c4bd9d1dbd37321cf9196d95fd977ab84d38","tid":631962,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180417/20364011?_ga=2.7470130.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F20364011%3F_ga%3D2.7470130.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=HpNC7wmU2S%2F5YZmBUwkU6zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=fa937e06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F20364011%3F_ga%3D2.7470130.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=92d72b44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180417/20364011?_ga=2.7470130.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n自由黨黨慶CY甩底　<br />\n田少捐金牛撐屠狼 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n3.2K<br />\n專欄專論<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180417/large/17lp2p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180417%2Flarge%2F17lp2p4.jpg&h=5453edbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n田少攞出金牛撐阿廷查UGL案，話要還CY一個「公道」。<br />\n<br />\n自由黨噚晚舉行25周年黨慶，現任特首林鄭月娥一改過去梁振英杯葛該黨黨慶做法，同三司及多名局長畀面到場，其間自由黨黨魁鍾國斌一度預告689會以政協副主席身份到場，點知酒會開始後就傳出689甩底消息，至酒會結束仍未見影，一向狙擊689不遺餘力嘅自由黨榮譽主席田北俊就寸爆CY，可能因為「天下為公」眾籌反應太理想而唔嚟。<br />\n<br />\n田少最初得聞CY會到場，重提當年佢帶頭杯葛自由黨，繼而又話對於對方唔再做特首好高興，「我都唔係幾知佢呢個政協副主席做乜，可能出席吓我哋呢啲酒會都唔錯啊！」亦指林鄭做特首後，社會和諧好多，搞笑話唔會要林鄭捐款畀該黨，「自由黨係富貴黨吖嘛，點會叫行政長官捐錢畀我哋呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180417/large/a1204a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180417%2Flarge%2Fa1204a.gif&h=f9a3e2be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n噚晚娥特仲同來賓、自由黨員預演埋《國歌法》下聽國歌嘅禮儀。 　王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n娥特同司局長到場「大和解」<br />\n<br />\n最終689甩底，田少有獨特見解，向同場嘅民主黨林卓廷話對方突然改變主意，可能因得知「天下為公」籌款初步達標，阿廷乘勢叫田少捐錢支持，田少即刻喺銀包攞出一張金牛，仲話相信計劃200萬都唔夠使，叫阿廷努力搵多啲有錢佬支持，要阿廷努力「還CY一個公道」。<br />\n<br />\n黨魁鍾國斌致辭時話特首同司局長都出席，證明該黨同特區政府關係非常好；黨慶主持楊哲安則叫在場賓客影相後，放上網hashtag「大合照」就得，唔使用「大和解」，令台上嘅娥特都笑埋一份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"2a562839ff4bde4d5747f74e84b60838110c23e1","tid":631962,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T03:33:38.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}